.br
RFCs 4250, 4251, 4252, 4253, 4254, and 4419
.SH BUGS
.I Sshsession
shouldn't have to run as the host owner and using
.IR factotum (4)
correctly would permit this.
.PP
The SSH v2 protocol is a classic second system:
over-engineered,
overly complicated,
misdesigned
and
jammed full of pointless goodies.
